<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Sulzbach</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Anweisung von Engelhard Kellner, Bürger zu Sulzbach, die Klage um Güter vor dem Landgericht gegen Konrad II. Mendel und die Brüder Peter, Georg I. und Stefan I. Tetzel, alle Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen eines Testaments der angeblich verstorbenen Klara Tetzel zurückzunehmen, weil sie noch lebt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_332_r2l19">Sulcʒbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_332_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt / <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mendell der <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l21">Peter / Görg vnd Steffan die Tecʒell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l22">daʒ Jn Engelhart Kellner <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> mitburger / 
<del rend="strikethrough">das i </del> Jre gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l23">auf dıe <expan>lantſchran<ex>ne</ex></expan> cʒu Sulcʒbach geladen hab / von eins ge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l24">ſcheffts wegen / als fraw Clar dıe Jobs Tecʒlın <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l25">getan ſülle <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Nu <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ dıe <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l26">fraw Clar dıe Tecʒlin noch lebt / vnd ſıe <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l27">von <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> geſcheffte vviſſen / daʒ ſıe getan hab / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l28">daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran weyſen wöllet / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l29">Er von der klag auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantgerihte laſʒ / vnd het Er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l30">den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> oder Jr <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> beſunder ıcht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eʒ <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l31">
<add><ab facs="#facs_332_line_1576487989333_5124">von 
<del rend="strikethrough">des g </del> eins </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l6">geſcheffts </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l7"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> oder </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l8">worumb das </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l9">wer </ab></add> <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l32"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſlewnigs <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l33">ſo <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> anheim ſein / vnd tut darynne <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l34"><expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in <expan>ſölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l35"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ın <expan>vıg<ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan>Nat<ex>iuitatis</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>ea</ex>te</expan> <expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ıe</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Sulczbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mendell der
                            <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex></expan> und Peter, Görg und Steffan die Teczell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie daz in Engelhart Kellner,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> mitburger, ire gut auf die
                                <expan>lantschran<ex>ne</ex></expan> czu Sulczbach geladen hab von
                        eins gescheffts wegen, als fraw Clar die Jobs Teczlin,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin, getan sülle
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Nu <expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> wissen, daz die
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> fraw Clar die Teczlin noch lebt und sie
                                <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie von
                            <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> gescheffte wissen, daz sie getan hab.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran weysen wöllet, daz er von der klag
                        auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantgerihte lasz. Und het er
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu den
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> oder ir <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        besunder icht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ez
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>von eins gescheffts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> oder worumb das
                            wer</add>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                                <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan>, so <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> anheim sein. Und tut darynne
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir in <expan>sölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>nat<ex>ivitatis</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ea</ex>te</expan>
<expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ie</expan>.</ab>
</div>
